<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Architecture — {project}</title>
<style>
  html, body { margin: 0; height: 100%; }
  .wrap { position: fixed; inset: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; background: #05060a; }
  #cy { background: #05060a; }
  .bar { padding: 8px 12px; font: 13px system-ui, sans-serif; color: #c9d1d9; background: #0a0c11; border-bottom: 1px solid #23292f; }
  .bar button { margin: 0 2px; padding: 3px 9px; font-size: 12px; background: #172431; color: #cfe3f7; border: 1px solid #2e455c; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
  .bar button:hover { background: #2c4256; }
  .hint { color: #7d8590; font-size: 11px; margin-left: 6px; }
  #cy { flex: 1; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="bar">
    <strong>{project}</strong> architecture &nbsp;·&nbsp;
    <span id="nodes">?</span> modules, <span id="edges">?</span> import edges &nbsp;·&nbsp;
    <button id="expandAll">expand all</button>
    <button id="collapseAll">collapse all</button>
    <button id="reset">reset view</button>
    <span class="hint">click a box = drill one level in · click an open package = fold it · right-click any node = focus (spotlight its deps, dims the rest) · click empty space = clear · arrow [n] = summed import count</span>
  </div>
  <div id="cy"></div>
</div>
<script>/*__CYTOSCAPE__*/</script>
<script>/*__LAYOUT_BASE__*/</script>
<script>/*__COSE_BASE__*/</script>
<script>/*__FCOSE__*/</script>
<script>/*__VIEWER__*/</script>
</body>
</html>
